This is my email address.

00:18:04.180 --> 00:18:08.099
I am part of what's called the Data Science Lab at Fred Hutch.

00:18:08.099 --> 00:18:15.859
We basically do all sorts of courses in education, and there are other members of the Data Science

00:18:15.859 --> 00:18:16.859
Lab here.

00:18:16.859 --> 00:18:23.979
I'm not going to make you raise your hand, but thanks all for being here.

00:18:23.979 --> 00:18:29.060
Other links, website, this talk, and all of these kinds of resources that I've talked

00:18:29.060 --> 00:18:30.060
about.

00:18:30.060 --> 00:18:31.060
And that's all I have.

00:18:31.060 --> 00:18:32.060
Thank you.

